{"type":"message","id":"c6a291a3","parentId":"65d56862","timestamp":"2026-03-26T23:00:00.344Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:10a19bb7-7afb-4b24-8478-62555b540c2d daily-ping-telegram] Send daily ping to Telegram with this EXACT format:\n\n🌅 Daily Ping — {DAY}, {MMM} {DD}, {YYYY}\n\n💰 Bitcoin\n• Price: ${BTC_PRICE} USD\n• 24h: {BTC_CHANGE}% {TREND}\n\n📊 Tech Stocks\n• NVDA: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• MSFT: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• GOOGL: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• INTC: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• META: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• AMD: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n\n📊 Market: S&P {SPX}, Nasdaq {NDX} — {BRIEF_COMMENTARY}\n\n🚀 Trending GitHub Repos (Created Since 2025)\n1. {repo} ⭐ {stars}K\n... (top 10)\n\n— ⏰ {HH}:{MM} SGT | Data: CoinGecko, Yahoo Finance, GitHub API\n\nFetch fresh data using:\n- Bitcoin: CoinGecko API (price + 24h change)\n- Stocks: Yahoo Finance (NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD)\n- Indices: S&P 500 and NasdaqComposite\n- GitHub: top 10 repos created since 2025, sorted by stars\n\nSend to Telegram target 1087368827 using the message tool.\nCurrent time: Friday, March 27th, 2026 — 7:00 AM (Asia/Singapore) / 2026-03-26 23:00 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774566000342}}
{"type":"message","id":"cc42e03d","parentId":"c6a291a3","timestamp":"2026-03-26T23:04:04.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user wants me to send a daily ping to Telegram with specific formatting. I need to:\n\n1. Fetch Bitcoin price and 24h change from CoinGecko\n2. Fetch stock prices for NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD from Yahoo Finance\n3. Fetch S&P 500 and Nasdaq indices\n4. Fetch top 10 trending GitHub repos created since 2025 with stars\n5. Format the message exactly as specified\n6. Send to Telegram target 1087368827\n\nLet me start by fetching all the data I need. I'll make async calls where possible.\n\nFirst, let me understand the exact format required:\n- Date header with day, month day, year\n- Bitcoin: price and 24h change with trend emoji\n- Tech stocks: NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD with prices, change % and trend\n- Market indices: S&P 500 and Nasdaq\n- Trending GitHub repos since 2025\n- Timestamp at the end\n\nLet me make","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" I'll fetch the data and send the daily ping to Telegram. Let me gather"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.web_fetch:0","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin&vs_currencies=usd&include_24hr_change=true","extractMode":"text"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.web_fetch:1","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://query1.finance.yahoo.com/v8/finance/chart/^GSPC,^IXIC,NVDA,MSFT,GOOGL,INTC,META,AMD?interval=1d&range=2d","extractMode":"text"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.web_fetch:2","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=created:>2025-01-01&sort=stars&order=desc&per_page=10","extractMode":"text"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":16593,"output":419,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17012,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cach